VM2	KP2.pem
🔥 IMPORTANT CONCEPT
To transfer file:
VM1 → VM2
VM1 must have:
KP2.pem
because VM2 authenticates using its own key pair.

🌐 COMPLETE FLOW
MacBook
↓
SSH into VM1 using KP1.pem
↓
